                            <comment id="14088468" author="jmspaggi" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2014 23:34:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think user&apos;s question was more related to the logic behind doing manual splits more than the way to do it. Like, under which use-case do we want to do a manual split. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not sure we want to document that deep.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14089278" author="busbey" created="Thu, 7 Aug 2014 14:41:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would definitely like us to have docs on common ops needs, such as handling manual splits.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
